ael Martin,\n3) While Michael Martin is looking down observe that his neck does not attach to his body.\n\nExpected Results:\nAll head\'s and bodies must not separate.','jhh\nassigned\nreassigned\ntesting\n','test\n','Fri 14th November 2008 18:03:33 TBog changed:<li>the assignment to TBog</li><br>'),(4043,1223164800,0,0,0,0,0,0,1,6,2,5,1223078400,0,0,0,3,'(40%-49%)','Occasionally - Crash - Gameplay - Results - Preliminary Match: Upon enterering the results screen for a preliminary match the game appeared to crash.','Summary:\nOccasionally, during gameplay, Results, Preliminary Match, when the User completed a preliminary match for a 7 vs 7 tournament, then proceeded to the results screen, the game appeared to crash.\n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n1) From the Main Menu, selected Continue,\n2) Selected Career Mode,\n3) Selected Tournament,\n4) Selected any 7 vs 7tournament with a preliminary match,\n5) Finished preliminary match,\n6) Observed that the game appeared to crash.\n\nExpected Results:\nGame must not crash.\n\nNOTE(1): Two Xbox Xenon Crash Dumps are located on the FTP in the following location:\n\n/Paintball/X360 Crash Dumps\n\n- PB_#4043_01.rar\n- PB_#4043_02.rar\n\nNOTE(2): May be related to bug #4041.','jhh\n','[Alex Knight (AMP QA) -- 10/13/2008 09:18:37 AM]\nVerified 10.06.08 buildtest\n',''),(4051,1223251200,0,0,0,0,0,0,1,6,2,5,1223078400,0,0,0,3,'(1%-9%)','Occasionally (1%-9%) - Gameplay - Preliminary Match: When the opponents flag was taken to the User\'s Characters base the game appeared to crash.','Summary:\nOccasionally, during gameplay, preliminary match, when the User\'s Character returned to their own base with the opponents flag the game appeared to crash.\n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n1) From the Main Menu, selected Continue,\n2) Selected Career Mode,\n3) Selected Tournament,\n4) Selected a 7 vs 7 tournament with a preliminary match,\n5) Captured the opponents flag and return to base,\n6) Observed that the game appeared to crash.\n\nExpected Results:\nGam