ch and stutter. \n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n1) From the initial match start, switch the Marker from the right to the left,\n2) Observe the animation appears to twitch and stutter.\n\nExpected Results:\nThe in game animations must be smooth and not corrupt.','jhh\ntesting\n','test\n','Fri 14th November 2008 18:03:33 TBog changed:<li>the assignment to TBog</li><br>'),(4240,1223251200,0,0,0,0,0,1,1,4,4,5,1223078400,0,0,0,1,'(100%)','Video/Graphic - Gameplay: Switching the Marker from the right to the left hand causes the paintballs to appear to be coming out of the side of the barrel.','Summary:\nDuring gameplay, if the user switches hands, holding the paintball marker in the left hand the paintballs to appear to be coming out of the side of the barrel.\n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n1) From the initial match start, switch the Marker from the right to the left,\n2) Observe the paintballs to appear to be coming out of the side of the barrel.\n\nExpected Results:\nThe paintballs must not appear to be coming out of the side of the barrel..','jhh\ntesting\n','test\n','Fri 14th November 2008 18:03:33 TBog changed:<li>the assignment to TBog</li><br>'),(4245,1223251200,0,0,0,0,0,0,1,4,3,5,1223078400,0,0,0,1,'(100%)','Video/Graphic - Gameplay: The 3-2-1-GO prompt interferes with the sight of the User.','Summary:\nDuring gameplay, if the User starts any match in any level, the User observes the 3-2-1-GO prompt appears to obstruct the view of the User as it is set right in the center of the Users aiming reticle.\n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n1) From the main menu, select any game mode,\n2) Select any level,\n3) At the start of the match, observe the 3-2-1-GO prompt obstructs the User\'s view.\n\nExpected Results:\nThe 3-2-1-GO prompt must not obstruct the User\'s view.','jhh\n','test\n',''),(4258,1223251200,0,0,0,0,2,0,1,17,3,1,1223164800,0,0,0,1,'(100%)','Options - Autosave appears set to ON when it is actually OFF.','Summary:\nIn the Options menu, if the autosave option was turned off at any 